{"id": 3129, "genre": 1001, "title": "最近你都经历了哪些“年前综合症”？", "description": "来说说过年前你都有哪些“小确不适”。（题图来自：iStock ©️ frimages）", "record_count": 502, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20200120130614cSRIUKky7P9EeGfi.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2020-01-21T17:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 352004, "content": "一边消极怠工一边【新的一年要变得更好哦！】的想法", "image": null, "praise_count": 160, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 720773}, {"id": 352005, "content": "想赶紧放假的焦虑叠加只放7天马上又要上班的焦虑", "image": null, "praise_count": 90, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 921335}, {"id": 352007, "content": "一边要和家人团聚一边考虑回答各种“灵魂拷问”的焦虑", "image": null, "praise_count": 43, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1123342}, {"id": 352008, "content": "想到要被迫回老家就烦得不得了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1289571}, {"id": 352009, "content": "想想要面对一堆亲戚不想过年了", "image": null, "praise_count": 35, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668637}, {"id": 352010, "content": "想好好休息但是知道过年是休息不了的焦虑", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1616850}, {"id": 352011, "content": "近十年来第一次过年不出门旅行；在家呆着感觉无聊至极……", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 118083}, {"id": 352012, "content": "各种应酬和过年购物的烦恼", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1065969}, {"id": 352014, "content": "年前的巨型工作还未结束。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1329728}, {"id": 352015, "content": "我想静静", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1588326}, {"id": 352017, "content": "上门拜访，挑时、备礼、谈吐。", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1582793}, {"id": 352529, "content": "年前就在担心疫情了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1271976}, {"id": 352018, "content": "想跟自己父母过年，想跟自己父母过年，已婚妇女的灵魂呐喊！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1028056}, {"id": 352019, "content": "总觉得家里哪里还没收拾好", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1017835}, {"id": 352020, "content": "我才发现2019年的一整年里我从来没有试图去了解是哪个生肖年。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1645551}, {"id": 352021, "content": "一想到各种“催”就失眠", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1234937}, {"id": 352022, "content": "感慨一年比一年过得快", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1677779}, {"id": 352027, "content": "想找一个没有爸妈的地方过年", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1663789}, {"id": 352283, "content": "每次过年感觉都是一片虚伪，各种繁文缛节压的完全透不过气，明明内心不一定开心，却要为了适应节日气氛而带上面具。可是，哪天不是带着面具呢！", "image": "img/option/option/202002191208157p0fC4Uv5ruet8GH", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1679194}, {"id": 352028, "content": "一想到回家要个家里的亲戚、长辈的朋友们social就觉得很麻烦", "image": "img/option/option/20200122235543BiIGg5aYe41dPrwz", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1351051}, {"id": 352034, "content": "病毒啊啊口罩", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1664504}, {"id": 352044, "content": "害怕放鞭炮🧨", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1513949}, {"id": 352301, "content": "因为单位不能听停转，所以我们每年都不知道什么时候开始放假，每次都是一半人突如其来被休息，完全没有时间给你买票确定地方旅游的余地。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1680379}, {"id": 352050, "content": "期末考试的紧张", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1151437}, {"id": 352063, "content": "没有按照计划做完想做的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1443917}, {"id": 352067, "content": "永遠無法妥帖安排家人朋友愛人的相處時間", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1582791}, {"id": 352637, "content": "缺失的2020", "image": "img/option/option/20200915180529BrOKU0jSyL6TfVIh", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "auth